"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月16日消息，对冲基金桥水基金创始人瑞·达利欧表示，自己相信[区块链](https://www.bitcoin86.com/block/)技术，而该技术将带来一场革命，并取得了公信力。达利欧称，[比特币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)取得了卓越的成就，从其被发明开始，一直以独特的方式工作并运转无误。虽然自己不是比特币专家，但比特币作为投资组合的一部分具备其优越性。而比特币几乎是年轻一代人心目中的黄金替代品，尽管黄金是法币体系下成熟的蓝筹资产。（marketwatch）\",\"timestamp\":1639813184,\"title\":\"达利欧：区块链将带来一场革命，它已经取得公信力\"},\"digest\":\"ygGlDO-9NZM4jeNv8RTyowkKC7HJ62bodX6yWV2MV7s\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xCCA6E098Da5B502C2fF6a61785Cd7c70091E334a\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"-PZa2SvWF8RJ9-gfSkZ9EhUfmuOt0BlC566kf3FeKls\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"EhTA8ay1MqwARbVBQoKXRbUbkUtHUsFJnixtug_fJE8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Ejwr6TlWPfjxtsbWINPk_rn79AH9atyZvr7_hbC0VlG7JpImvj8UI-FRWQOTWzX1LK6Tj4js3fC6JcoGYRhDCA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x5730064b41540215c552dc25c6d557dc775b7db4765cf10f3c581236bb6c075a62d709a0323715cba9b3c6881af62c61821d1c96d42d8213292883b42e7999001c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"-PZa2SvWF8RJ9-gfSkZ9EhUfmuOt0BlC566kf3FeKls\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"EhTA8ay1MqwARbVBQoKXRbUbkUtHUsFJnixtug_fJE8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"ygGlDO-9NZM4jeNv8RTyowkKC7HJ62bodX6yWV2MV7s\"}"